dashboard to see current threat indicators and assess our exposure status.\\n"'}, {'role': 'user', 'content': '"You can now produce your next sequence of actions for this turn, in order, and finish with DONE."'}, {'role': 'user', 'content': '{"stimuli": [{"type": "CONVERSATION", "content": "Acknowledged. I\'m moving to immediate incident response mode. Let me pull up the SIEM dashboard to see current threat indicators and assess our exposure status.", "source": "security_analyst_0"}]}'}]
